values: Just wanted to repost this in a public entry. This is my resource/credit post, my list of resources can be found here in my memories . If you find that I've used something you made (ie: a brush, texture, etc..) please comment here and let me know, I'll be happy to make sure I add it for credit :)

Quick post real quick to remind people here that Xanga annoys me to NO end. I just found out a girl has been taking all my icons and posting them in her journal. As far as LJ Land I didn't really care about credit in LJ Land, but after seeing that, I have made new rules about my stuff. Make sure to read them :

http://mykindofmusic.livejournal.com/profile

This is my graphics journal, and I don't like having my stuff hotlinked-therefore this journal is Friends Only. If you'd like to friend me, leave me a comment here and I'll make sure to comment and friend ya back! Please check out my userinfo for rules :]

Just wanted to let those interested know who you can expect graphics of here.
